    {
        "argon": "Argon"
    },
    {
        ".     Samarium is quite electropositive and reacts slowly with cold water and quite quickly with hot water to form samarium hydroxide:   :2 Sm + 6 H 2 O → 2 Sm 3 + 3 H 2     Samarium dissolves readily in dilute ": null
